@startuml UAV_GCS_DataFlow_Sequences
!theme plain
title Data Flow & Communication Sequences\nAutonomous UAV GCS System

' ============================================================================
' STYLE DEFINITIONS
' ============================================================================

skinparam BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam DefaultFontSize 9
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #000000
skinparam SequenceGroupBorderColor #01579B
skinparam SequenceGroupHeaderBackgroundColor #81D4FA

' ============================================================================
' MAIN SEQUENCE DIAGRAM: TELEMETRY DOWN + MISSION COMMAND UP
' ============================================================================

participant "Pixhawk 6C\nFlight Controller" as Pixhawk
participant "LoRa Module\n(UAV)" as LoRaAir
participant "LoRa Module\n(GCS)" as LoRaGnd
participant "MAVProxy\nHub" as MAVProxy
participant "Mission\nPlanner" as MP
participant "ROS2\nTelemetry Pub" as ROS_Telem
participant "Custom GCS\nSoftware" as CustomGCS
participant "DroneKit" as DroneKit

== SCENARIO 1: TELEMETRY DOWNLOAD (UAV → GCS) ==

autonumber

Pixhawk ->> Pixhawk: Generate telemetry\n(GPS, attitude, battery)\nevery 10-20ms
Pixhawk ->> LoRaAir: UART TX\nMAVLink packet\n(57600 baud)
note right of LoRaAir: Buffer telemetry\nfor RF modulation

LoRaAir ->> LoRaAir: LoRa modulation\n(SF7, 2.1KB/s)
note over LoRaAir, LoRaGnd: AIR TIME: 50-200ms\n915 MHz link\nLine-of-sight up to 30km

LoRaAir -->> LoRaGnd: LoRa RF signal\n(915 MHz)
note right of LoRaGnd: Demodulate RF\nto serial data

LoRaGnd ->> LoRaGnd: UART RX\nMAVLink packet received
LoRaGnd ->> MAVProxy: USB/COM3 Serial\ntelemetry stream
note right of MAVProxy: Parse MAVLink\nBroadcast to clients

par Parallel Distribution
    MAVProxy ->> MP: TCP:14550\ntelemetry stream
    note left of MP: Real-time monitoring\nParameter display
    
    MAVProxy ->> ROS_Telem: TCP:14551\ntelemetry stream
    note left of ROS_Telem: Deserialize MAVLink\nConvert to ROS message
    
    MAVProxy ->> MAVProxy: Log to file\n(.tlog, .bin)
end

ROS_Telem ->> ROS_Telem: Parse packet\nPublish to ROS topic
ROS_Telem ->> CustomGCS: ROS Topic Subscription\n/vehicle/telemetry\n(1-10 Hz effective rate)

CustomGCS ->> CustomGCS: Update state estimate\nTelemetry processing\nFeed to decision logic

note over Pixhawk, CustomGCS: TOTAL LATENCY: 150-420ms\n(LoRa air: 50-200ms + processing: ~100-220ms)

== SCENARIO 2: MISSION COMMAND UPLOAD (GCS → UAV) ==

autonumber

CustomGCS ->> CustomGCS: Decision logic\ncomputes next action\n(every 100-500ms)
note right of CustomGCS: Based on:\n• Telemetry state\n• Vision inference\n• Mission plan

CustomGCS ->> CustomGCS: Generate MAVLink\ncommand packet\n(SET_POSITION_TARGET,\nSET_ATTITUDE_TARGET, etc)

CustomGCS ->> DroneKit: ROS Topic Publish\n/mission/commands

DroneKit ->> DroneKit: DroneKit library\nConverts to MAVLink\ncommand packet

DroneKit ->> MAVProxy: TCP:14552\nMAVLink command\n(command upload)
note right of MAVProxy: Queue command\nfor transmission

MAVProxy ->> LoRaGnd: USB/COM3 Serial\ncommand packet\n(57600 baud)

LoRaGnd ->> LoRaGnd: UART TX\nMAVLink command

LoRaGnd ->> LoRaGnd: LoRa modulation\n(SF7, 2.1KB/s)

LoRaGnd -->> LoRaAir: LoRa RF signal\n(915 MHz)
note over LoRaGnd, LoRaAir: AIR TIME: 50-200ms

LoRaAir ->> LoRaAir: Demodulate\nUART RX\ncommand packet

LoRaAir ->> Pixhawk: UART RX\nMAVLink command\n(57600 baud)

Pixhawk ->> Pixhawk: Parse command\nUpdate flight controller state\n(servo output, mode change, etc)

note over CustomGCS, Pixhawk: TOTAL LATENCY: 150-420ms\n(LoRa air: 50-200ms + processing: ~100-220ms)

== SCENARIO 3: VIDEO STREAM (UAV → GCS) ==

autonumber

participant "Siyi A8 Mini\nCamera" as SiyiCamera
participant "Siyi HM30 Air\nEncoder" as SiyiAir
participant "Siyi HM30 Ground\nReceiver" as SiyiGnd
participant "ROS2\nVideo Pub" as ROS_Video

SiyiCamera ->> SiyiCamera: Capture frame\n30 FPS (33ms per frame)

SiyiCamera ->> SiyiAir: GigE Ethernet\nVideo data\n(1 Gbps link)

SiyiAir ->> SiyiAir: H.264/H.265 encoding\nVideo compression

SiyiAir ->> SiyiAir: Wireless encoding\n(Siyi proprietary 2.4GHz)

SiyiAir -->> SiyiGnd: 2.4GHz RF link\n(proprietary protocol)
note over SiyiAir, SiyiGnd: TYPICAL LATENCY: 20-100ms\nDepends on resolution & bitrate

SiyiGnd ->> SiyiGnd: Demodulate\nDecode video stream

SiyiGnd ->> ROS_Video: Ethernet output\ncompressed video data

ROS_Video ->> ROS_Video: Decode/decompress\nExtract frames\nPublish to ROS

ROS_Video ->> CustomGCS: ROS Topic Subscription\n/camera/frames\n(20-30 FPS)

CustomGCS ->> CustomGCS: OpenCV preprocessing\n(resize, normalize)

CustomGCS ->> CustomGCS: YOLOv8 inference\n(30-50ms per frame on CPU)

CustomGCS ->> CustomGCS: Decision based on detections\nUpdate mission state

note over SiyiCamera, CustomGCS: TOTAL VIDEO LATENCY: 80-200ms\n(Siyi: 20-100ms + encoding/decoding + inference: 30-100ms)

== SCENARIO 4: MISSION PLANNER PARAMETER TUNING ==

autonumber

MP ->> MAVProxy: TCP:14550\nParameter read request\n(PARAM_REQUEST_LIST)

MAVProxy ->> LoRaGnd: Relay to serial\nparameter request

LoRaGnd ->> LoRaAir: LoRa TX\nparameter request

LoRaAir ->> Pixhawk: UART RX\nparameter request

Pixhawk ->> Pixhawk: Retrieve parameter\nfrom memory

Pixhawk ->> LoRaAir: UART TX\nparameter value\n(PARAM_VALUE message)

LoRaAir ->> LoRaGnd: LoRa RX\nparameter value

LoRaGnd ->> MAVProxy: USB/COM3\nparameter value

MAVProxy ->> MP: TCP:14550\nparameter display

MP ->> MP: Display in GUI\nParameter tree

note right of MP: User adjusts PID gains\nor flight parameters

MP ->> MAVProxy: TCP:14550\nParameter write\n(PARAM_SET message)

MAVProxy ->> LoRaGnd: USB/COM3\nparameter write

LoRaGnd ->> LoRaAir: LoRa TX\nparameter set

LoRaAir ->> Pixhawk: UART RX\nset parameter value

Pixhawk ->> Pixhawk: Update parameter\nin memory

Pixhawk ->> Pixhawk: Take effect\n(new tuning applied)

note over MP, Pixhawk: PARAMETER TUNING LATENCY: 300-800ms\n(2x LoRa round-trip + processing)

== SCENARIO 5: CRITICAL COMMAND EXECUTION ==

autonumber

CustomGCS ->> CustomGCS: DECISION: ARM and TAKEOFF
note right of CustomGCS: OpenCV detected\nsuitable conditions

CustomGCS ->> DroneKit: /mission/commands\narm_drone() call

DroneKit ->> DroneKit: Convert to\nCOMMAND_LONG message

DroneKit ->> MAVProxy: TCP:14552\ncommand (ARM_DISARM)

MAVProxy ->> LoRaGnd: USB/COM3\ncommand

LoRaGnd ->> LoRaAir: LoRa TX\nARM command

LoRaAir ->> Pixhawk: UART RX\nARM_DISARM command

Pixhawk ->> Pixhawk: Process arm request\nverify conditions\n(pre-arm checks)

Pixhawk ->> Pixhawk: Arm motors\nReady for flight

Pixhawk ->> LoRaAir: UART TX\nSTATUSEXT (armed=1)

LoRaAir ->> LoRaGnd: LoRa TX\nstatus message

LoRaGnd ->> MAVProxy: USB/COM3\nstatus update

MAVProxy ->> ROS_Telem: TCP:14551\nstatus

ROS_Telem ->> CustomGCS: /vehicle/telemetry\narmed = true

CustomGCS ->> CustomGCS: Confirm arm state\nproceed to takeoff

note over CustomGCS, Pixhawk: COMMAND EXECUTION LATENCY: 200-500ms\n(LoRa + processing + Pixhawk response)

@enduml
